Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:08.97,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂 歡 節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱方法你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系統很簡單 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這嗎 可別搞壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 抬起手臂看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系統已經掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報支援系統在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過電腦進行的戰況分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己看著辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就這樣移動到環流銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 要安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在環上開出洞來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示當前位置 固定坐標值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快重新站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求情報支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像游泳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體放鬆就能浮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不會游泳就先說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到機體會如此不聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 宇宙中沒有海嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 我們去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是你點的少女套餐和紫菜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只要這些就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他好吃的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的事不用沮喪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也經常搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德你可以再放輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放輕鬆？要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大玩特玩一場就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天開始就是祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你得表現出覺得好吃的表情才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好吃的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 你還沒換衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話 好男人都會被搶走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 帥哥在這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算霸佔人家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒一起去參觀祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕魚的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機可單獨執行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉可繼續待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這次開自己的人形機器人來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機並非人形機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是Machine Caliber-K6821
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志願參加捕魚任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員雷德少尉正在視察祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那小子不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始執行海洋生物的捕捉任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拿網去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你之前完全沉下海了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber在替我幹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 來稍微陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你不知道怎麼花錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 這次我就特別請你吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就當作示範吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫菜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特選晚餐兩人份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 特選晚餐兩人份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 思鄉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回到宇宙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那也沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的生活如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和大家之間的距離 很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃紫菜麵包當然是這樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都討厭紫菜麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙太沒存在感了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒存在感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 就沒什麼想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回歸同盟的戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指在你現在所在的地方 在這艘船上想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己想要什麼都不知道 怎麼能得到別人的信賴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我合夥打撈船隻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打撈船隻？工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那個破廢鐵一定能撈到大寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算賺到錢 工資也花不完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 賺到錢就去吃好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等賺到更多的錢 就去搞艘更好的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢放在手裡也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要像這樣去實現自己的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現…自己的慾望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搶著挖人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶著挖人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要合夥的話 應該找專職的我才是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你培養成一流的船隻打撈師的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打撈船隻的事 我不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很簡單 我會教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 不懂的地方只管問就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不知道怎麼做 那就有樣學樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聽她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合夥 好吃的要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會教你如何辨別潮汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有資質 很快就能學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合夥的話 好酒隨便你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子還得教你游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子的屁股隨便摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 你從剛剛開始就很下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 你這貝殼屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是貝殼屁股啊 你這旱鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是旱鴨子 只是不會潛水罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 這是您的主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亞斯 人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殲滅對象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是章魚罷了 很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是光看到這小章魚就吃驚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上鯨烏賊還不得嚇趴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚 能吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機請求駕駛員雷德少尉支援
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part2 start
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力振蕩 展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.35,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(594,650)}Gravity Waver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也好 你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在想些啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營養學上沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法應對目前情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機請求雷德少尉支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全都成肉泥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 用網來撈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看別人是怎麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要盡可能大的網
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及請求其他人形機器人的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺能幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得意個啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子飽飽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電：我只能幫你到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 索敵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍檢測到能量反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險級別：低
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是光幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環流銀河消失的時候便會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛子還得好好練習才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習？ 艾米 你練過舞蹈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看 艾米 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就當作剛剛的回禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 身體還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 雷德哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺錢 付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起 吃好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拿到的報酬是扶持了別人的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扶持了別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人邀請我去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Chamber一起打撈船隻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為海裡沉著很多東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以知道這顆星球以前發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去打撈船隻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能來真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你肯定會去皮尼歐那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有些東西 希望貝羅茲教我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這台人形機器人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是好像很快就會沒東西可教了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事 我想學到更多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這個也中了
